Functional requirements
Users of the system should be able to login and logout of the system
It should be able to generate a log with a timestamp of the times that employees logged in and out of the system.
The system should pop up a message indicating the time the employee reported and left the hospital.
The system should add the profile of new employees.
Employees should be able to view their profile

Non-functional requirements
The system should have a user-friendly interface
The system should be secured by applying the rule of least priviledge.
The system should be robust that is able to recovery from the errors.
security is associated with user authentication.

Actors 
Administrator
Doctors
Nurses

Technologies
python 


